reviews.review_text:
Right Loge = private 8 seat box overlooking stage   Thanks to Fred Fier we had our whole crew in that loge.
akg's d1000e on loan from Charlie DiSalvo and Jerry Moore.  great job on transfer, still looking for the show of the 9th (left loge) which disapeared from its box in 90's.
  My Sister Nancy was there with me for the only Dead show she saw.
